\begin{lemma}[Strong-Commutativity] If $R$ strongly commutes with $S$ then $R$ commutes with $S$.
\end{lemma}

\begin{proof}
Via the following ``chase'' diagram (probably well known?)

    % https://q.uiver.app/?
\[\begin{tikzcd}
	\bullet & \bullet & \bullet & \bullet \\
